{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-17","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-error-message-component","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 17","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada kada su stilovi primenjeni na element <code>div</code>, vreme je da primenimo neke stilove i na element <code>p</code>.</p>\n<p>Trenutno, boja teksta za paragrafski element je crna. Ali bilo bi lepo da je boja umesto toga tamno crvena.</p>\n<p>U ranijem koraku, naučili ste kako da radite sa bojama pozadine kao što je ovo: <code>bg-red-100</code>. Sličnu stvar možete uraditi i sa bojom teksta prateći ovaj obrazac: <code>text-color-shade</code>.</p>\n<p>Evo primera kako primeniti plavu boju teksta na element:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;p class=\"text-blue-500\">This has blue text.&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Počnite dodavanjem atributa klase na vaš <code>p</code> element. Zatim primenite odgovarajuću utilitarnu klasu za postavljanje crvene boje teksta sa nijansom postavljenoj na <code>700</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"684d11ffd15a531225d081e9","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-17"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Error Message Component</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  </head>\n  <body>  \n    <div class=\"bg-red-100 border-2 border-red-300 rounded-md md:w-1/2 p-4 mt-4 md:mx-auto flex gap-4 justify-center\">\n      <p>\n        <strong>Error!</strong> Something went wrong. Please try again.\n      </p>\n      <button aria-label=\"Dismiss\">\n        <span aria-hidden>&times;</span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[10,12],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>p</code> element bi trebalo da ima atribut class.</p>","testString":"const pEl = document.querySelector(\"p\");\nassert.isTrue(pEl?.hasAttribute(\"class\"));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš otvarajući <code>p</code> tag bi trebalo da ima <code>text-red-700</code> alat class.</p>","testString":"const pEl = document.querySelector(\"p\");\nassert.isTrue(pEl?.classList.contains(\"text-red-700\"));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/#workshop-error-message-component","dashedName":"step-17","certification":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries-v9","chapter":"front-end-development-libraries","module":"css-libraries-and-frameworks","block":"workshop-error-message-component","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-18","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries-v9/workshop-error-message-component/step-16","id":"684d11ffd15a531225d081e9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Error Message Component</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.c